                            <div class="choose-content">
                                <div class="choose-title">
                                    <h2>Compliance Management</h2>
                                    <p>Compliance management is one of the crucial aspects of HR outsourcing services. Organisations can suffer immensely on failing to comply with employment laws and regulations. We help organisations stay away from any legal hassle by ensuring compliance with labour laws enacted by the Central Government and State Government. Kutumbh HRCare ensures your employees with statutory and contractual entitlements. Since the government can change employment laws over time, having a trusted HR partner like Kutumbh HRCare saves organisations much of their time understanding new laws and their complexities. Our compliance Management benefits our clients with</p>

                                    <p>
<ul>
<li>Reduced Cost </li>
<li>Efficient Risk Management</li>
<li>Enhanced Flexibility</li>
<li>Timely Submission of Challans & Returns as Per Government Laws</li>
<li>Keeping Clients Fully Compliant as Per the Requirements</li>
<li>Hassle-free Obtainment of Labour Licence </li>
<li>Adherence to PF, ESIC, PT, Gratuity, Bonus and WC & Minimum Wage Act</li>
</ul>
</p>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
